I want to create a HubSpot CTA button, and when the button is clicked, I want to redirect to an external page with the query string ?email={{contact.email}}
Is this possible to do? I tried to put a personalization token in the redirect URL but HubSpot says that url is invalid. See screenshot.



I tried to do this with a form, but the form requires at least the email field to be part of the form, but I don’t need that since the email address already exists in the contact in HubSpot
